41
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:17,360
ALL Aboard!

42
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:19,780
<i>(door closes)</i>

43
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,400
<i>(engine chugging)</i>

44
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:24,600
Goodbye! Goodbye, everypony!

45
00:02:25,010 --> 00:02:26,200
Fluttershy!

46
00:02:27,610 --> 00:02:31,460
